\pard\f0\fs28   Sect. TRACHYNIA (Link) Nyman ({\i Trachynia }Link). Annuals. Leaves flat, usually flaccid. Raceme short, stiffly erect, of 1-2(-6) spikelets. Spikelets laterally compressed. Glumes and lemmas coriaceous. Anthers not more than 1 mm.
